This leader even put the founders of IBM in the shadows - based on Watson's ideas to this day the unbeatable culture and identity of the company.
Watson led the company until 1952.
IBM, began, as the name has already betrayed, with the production and distribution of all possible machines for trade - from sausage and cheese cutters to cashiers.
